{"tid":638504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[垃圾政府廣告] 究竟而家香港個政府垃圾到去咩地步 ?","createTime":"2018-04-22T18:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T15:21:52.000Z","uid":37125,"like":121,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"4a27067fd98fb3b3604cf8d73703aa765292462f","tid":638504,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://steemitimages.com/0x0/https://gateway.ipfs.io/ipfs/QmVMnuQJxheezCsDiw8ayu4KvvvuLoTadTcuiTQ7xWkku3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteemitimages.com%2F0x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fgateway.ipfs.io%2Fipfs%2FQmVMnuQJxheezCsDiw8ayu4KvvvuLoTadTcuiTQ7xWkku3&h=33edf73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩料呀? 垃圾蟲 同 清潔龍 都唔識分呀? 你捉清潔龍嚟做乜鳩呀? 清潔龍本身就係清潔香港嘅象徵. 我知你班自以為破格嘅人諗緊啲咩. 但係你哋有冇諗過後果呀? 錢已袋就算呀? 噉樣玩隻清潔龍, 以後<span style=\"color: red;\">重</span>點樣搵佢嚟說服人呀!  <br />\n<br />\n哦~ 你班仆街又想玩去殖化呀? 唔係? 噉又唔見警察公共關係科用翻同樣手法嚟出個 Ad : &quot;犯法<span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>得走! <span style=\"color: red;\">重</span>捉你唔到.&quot;  (隻清潔龍換咗隻警察公仔) ?<br />\n<br />\n一個政府廣告嘅 target audience 係大眾, 大眾即係包含咗唔同階層嘅人. 得罪講句, 會亂拋垃圾嘅人會唔會睇得明/睇得到你個 hidden message 呀 ? (定還是只係我真心咗, 根本只係班友求鳩其將清潔龍當咗垃圾蟲嚟用) 不單止 message 方向錯晒, <span style=\"color: red;\">重</span>要錯字, 真係垃圾過垃圾蟲."},{"pid":"47000aa80f4f75d603cc3e334138634bfb18801e","tid":638504,"uid":41245,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:45:50.000Z","msg":"真係清潔龍嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真我唔係好記得清潔龍只係記得垃圾蟲<br />\n點解可以錯到咁徹底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捉返垃圾蟲唔得咩<br />\n起碼出名啲"},{"pid":"b2b0502a632b4458f603d3c2e74b0eb207375f9e","tid":638504,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47000aa80f4f75d603cc3e334138634bfb18801e","tid":638504,"uid":41245,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:45:50.000Z","msg":"真係清潔龍嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真我唔係好記得清潔龍只係記得垃圾蟲<br />\n點解可以錯到咁徹底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捉返垃圾蟲唔得咩<br />\n起碼出名啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:52:08.000Z","msg":"頭先問咗個90後, 佢竟然唔識清潔龍, 只係識垃圾蟲.<br />\n有冇人小學收過清潔龍張貼紙? 打去貼紙上面個電話會有故事聽. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f8cb3791ae769c5c9b93358aee00a7739a26c6","tid":638504,"uid":38671,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T19:03:40.000Z","msg":"呢隻係新版清潔龍，出左幾年就變垃圾龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2016/0921/20160921100601434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2016%2F0921%2F20160921100601434.jpg&h=ebc45db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊既係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FlbI3U9Q4JA/WlzowLSywNI/AAAAAAAAATA/hHvjWYMe2qIVElKISLN8VYN9BWN7Uf-KgCLcBGAs/s1600/%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%2B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-FlbI3U9Q4JA%2FWlzowLSywNI%2FAAAAAAAAATA%2FhHvjWYMe2qIVElKISLN8VYN9BWN7Uf-KgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F%2525E6%2525B8%252585%2525E6%2525BD%252594%252B%2525E6%2525B8%252585%2525E6%2525BD%252594%2525E9%2525BE%25258D%2525E5%2525AE%2525B6%2525E6%252597%25258F03.jpg&h=17d6246a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67be8d70a105b78005de19f635f587e9ee28a0b2","tid":638504,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64f8cb3791ae769c5c9b93358aee00a7739a26c6","tid":638504,"uid":38671,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T19:03:40.000Z","msg":"呢隻係新版清潔龍，出左幾年就變垃圾龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2016/0921/20160921100601434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2016%2F0921%2F20160921100601434.jpg&h=ebc45d